Class MyStack<E>

java.lang.Object
datastructures.MyArrayList<E>
datastructures.MyStack<E>
Type Parameters:
E - generic type that the stack will contain
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterator<E>, ListADT<E>, StackADT<E>, Serializable
public class MyStack<E> extends MyArrayList<E> implements StackADT<E>, Iterator<E>
enforces stack behavior on ArrayList parent datastructure stack behavior is last in first out, or lifo
